{
    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx",
    "path": "/blogs/Storybook 使用手册——MDX 和 Doc Blocks/",
    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"张小伦的网络日志","description":"欢迎来到张小伦的网络日志 \n\t\t一个记录生活，分享心得的博客","menu":[{"id":"home","name":"首页","url":"/"},{"id":"blog","name":"博文","url":"/blogs"},{"id":"category","name":"分类","url":"/categories"},{"id":"archive","name":"归档","url":"/archives"},{"id":"lab","name":"实验室","url":"/labs"},{"id":"about","name":"关于我","url":"/about"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"18f2f462-ade0-56ab-bfdd-19dab964e508","html":"<h2 class=\"heading subtitle heading\" id=\"MDX\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#MDX\" aria-label=\"MDX permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MDX</h2>\n<p class=\"para\">MDX是一种标准的文件格式，由Markdown和JSX组合而成，文件后缀是<code>.mdx</code>。也就是说你可以在MDX中使用Markdown的语法编写内容，同时还能嵌入JSX编写的组件。</p>\n<p class=\"para\">可以用MDX编写纯粹的文档，把文档和Story一起添加到Storybook中。</p>\n<p class=\"para\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e773e85a7fd2bdee1a6581275447531/1cfc2/4a487fd65b9f6a6b.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.25531914893617%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4a487fd65b9f6a6b\"\n        title=\"4a487fd65b9f6a6b\"\n        src=\"/static/1e773e85a7fd2bdee1a6581275447531/1d69c/4a487fd65b9f6a6b.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e773e85a7fd2bdee1a6581275447531/4dcb9/4a487fd65b9f6a6b.png 188w,\n/static/1e773e85a7fd2bdee1a6581275447531/5ff7e/4a487fd65b9f6a6b.png 375w,\n/static/1e773e85a7fd2bdee1a6581275447531/1d69c/4a487fd65b9f6a6b.png 750w,\n/static/1e773e85a7fd2bdee1a6581275447531/1cfc2/4a487fd65b9f6a6b.png 900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 class=\"heading subtitle heading\" id=\"Doc-Blocks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#Doc-Blocks\" aria-label=\"Doc Blocks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Doc Blocks</h2>\n<p class=\"para\">顾名思义，就是文档中的块。一个Story渲染成的文档就是由若干个Block组成的。在Storybook中有不少Block。常见的可能是ArgsTable，Canvas和Story。</p>\n<h3 class=\"heading\" id=\"ArgsTable\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ArgsTable\" aria-label=\"ArgsTable permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ArgsTable</h3>\n<p class=\"para\">Story自动识别组件的Props，自动生成一个表格。表格中会列出这些参数，同时还提供了可交互的参数控制</p>\n<p class=\"para\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/4352a/b231811d70405605.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"b231811d70405605\"\n        title=\"b231811d70405605\"\n        src=\"/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/1d69c/b231811d70405605.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/4dcb9/b231811d70405605.png 188w,\n/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/5ff7e/b231811d70405605.png 375w,\n/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/1d69c/b231811d70405605.png 750w,\n/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/78797/b231811d70405605.png 1125w,\n/static/682c93a076a587cd7d801127bb580a6b/4352a/b231811d70405605.png 1364w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p class=\"para\"><a href=\"https://storybook.js.org/386bdaed7a08de9d831f68e43e18142c/addon-controls-docs-optimized.mp4\" class=\"link-underline\">image</a></p>\n<h3 class=\"heading\" id=\"Canvas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#Canvas\" aria-label=\"Canvas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Canvas</h3>\n<p class=\"para\">提供包含了一个控制条的可交互的画板，内部包含了Source这个Block，用于展示代码</p>\n<p class=\"para\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 706px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a5918f9bd14bdebf335f5d8af99b70f/9f21b/e27abe97b638577c.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.25531914893617%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"e27abe97b638577c\"\n        title=\"e27abe97b638577c\"\n        src=\"/static/0a5918f9bd14bdebf335f5d8af99b70f/9f21b/e27abe97b638577c.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0a5918f9bd14bdebf335f5d8af99b70f/4dcb9/e27abe97b638577c.png 188w,\n/static/0a5918f9bd14bdebf335f5d8af99b70f/5ff7e/e27abe97b638577c.png 375w,\n/static/0a5918f9bd14bdebf335f5d8af99b70f/9f21b/e27abe97b638577c.png 706w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p class=\"para\">更多Block的信息可以参考<a href=\"https://storybook.js.org/docs/vue/writing-docs/doc-block-argstable\" class=\"link-underline\">这里</a>。</p>\n<h2 class=\"heading subtitle heading\" id=\"MDX的简单例子\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#MDX%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90\" aria-label=\"MDX的简单例子 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MDX的简单例子</h2>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">&lt;!-- Checkbox.stories.mdx --&gt;\n\nimport { Canvas, Meta, Story } from &#39;@storybook/addon-docs&#39;;\n\nimport Checkbox from &#39;./Checkbox.vue&#39;;\n\n&lt;Meta title=&quot;MDX/Checkbox&quot; component={Checkbox} /&gt;\n\nexport const Template = (args, { argTypes }) =&gt; ({\n  props: Object.keys(argTypes),\n  components: { Checkbox },\n  template: &#39;&lt;Checkbox v-bind=&quot;$props&quot; /&gt;&#39;,\n});\n\n# Checkbox\n\nWith `MDX`, we can define a story for `Checkbox` right in the middle of our\nMarkdown documentation.\n\n&lt;Canvas&gt;\n  &lt;Story \n    name=&quot;Unchecked&quot;\n    args={{ \n      label: &#39;Unchecked&#39;,\n    }}&gt;\n    {Template.bind({})}\n   &lt;/Story&gt;\n\n  &lt;Story \n    name=&quot;Checked&quot;\n    args={{ \n      label: &#39;Unchecked&#39;, \n      checked: true,\n    }}&gt;\n    {Template.bind({})}\n   &lt;/Story&gt;\n  \n  &lt;Story \n    name=&quot;Secondary&quot;\n    args={{\n      label: &#39;Secondary&#39;, \n      checked: true, \n      appearance: &#39;secondary&#39;,\n    }}&gt;\n    {Template.bind({})}\n   &lt;/Story&gt;\n&lt;/Canvas&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">最终会渲染在Storybook中，可以在页面的<code>Docs</code>中查看</p>\n<p class=\"para\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/71ba4/939bb6ee2afeb401.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.48936170212767%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"939bb6ee2afeb401\"\n        title=\"939bb6ee2afeb401\"\n        src=\"/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/1d69c/939bb6ee2afeb401.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/4dcb9/939bb6ee2afeb401.png 188w,\n/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/5ff7e/939bb6ee2afeb401.png 375w,\n/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/1d69c/939bb6ee2afeb401.png 750w,\n/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/78797/939bb6ee2afeb401.png 1125w,\n/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/aa440/939bb6ee2afeb401.png 1500w,\n/static/7ed0112ef910ee34c3dc0c1ae623c069/71ba4/939bb6ee2afeb401.png 1870w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p class=\"para\">可以看到，使用了<code>@storybook/addon-docs</code> 提供的几个组件：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p class=\"para\">Meta： 用于描述当前组件文档页面的信息</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"para\">Canvas：绘制Story渲染使用的画板</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"para\">Story：创建一个Story</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"para\">Story中用于配置的各项参数，都可以做为这几个组件各自的Props传入。比如，使用CSF文件时，我们这么写：</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">// Checkbox.stories.js|jsx|ts|tsx\n\nimport { Checkbox } from &#39;./Checkbox&#39;;\n\nexport default {\n  /* 👇 The title prop is optional.\n  * See https://storybook.js.org/docs/react/configure/overview#configure-story-loading\n  * to learn how to generate automatic titles\n  */\n  title: &#39;Checkbox&#39;,\n  component: Checkbox,\n};\n\nconst Template = (args) =&gt; ({\n  //👇 Your template goes here\n});\n\n\nexport const Unchecked = Template.bind({});\nUnchecked.args = {\n  label: &#39;Unchecked&#39;,\n};</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p class=\"para\">在使用MDX编写时，则是如下：</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" theme=\"one-dark\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">&lt;!-- Checkbox.stories.mdx --&gt;\n\nimport { Canvas, Meta, Story } from &#39;@storybook/addon-docs&#39;;\n\nimport Checkbox from &#39;./Checkbox.vue&#39;;\n\n&lt;Meta title=&quot;MDX/Checkbox&quot; component={Checkbox} /&gt;\n\nexport const Template = (args, { argTypes }) =&gt; ({\n  props: Object.keys(argTypes),\n  components: { Badge },\n  template: &#39;&lt;Badge v-bind=&quot;$props&quot; /&gt;&#39;,\n});\n\n&lt;Story\n  name=&quot;Unchecked&quot;\n  args={{\n    label: &#39;Unchecked&#39;,\n  }}&gt;\n  {Template.bind({})}\n&lt;/Story&gt;  </code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h2 class=\"heading subtitle heading\" id=\"单纯的MDX文件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E7%9A%84MDX%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"单纯的MDX文件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>单纯的MDX文件</h2>\n<p class=\"para\">通常，在使用Storybook MDX时，在MDX中定义Story，而文档会自动与这些Story关联。</p>\n<p class=\"para\">也可以编写不包含Story的MDX文档，将其与现有的Story相关联，或者将这个MDX作为文档节点嵌入Storybook的导航中。</p>\n<p class=\"para\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/bfe1f/d32bba18e172331c.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.93617021276595%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"d32bba18e172331c\"\n        title=\"d32bba18e172331c\"\n        src=\"/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/1d69c/d32bba18e172331c.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/4dcb9/d32bba18e172331c.png 188w,\n/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/5ff7e/d32bba18e172331c.png 375w,\n/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/1d69c/d32bba18e172331c.png 750w,\n/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/78797/d32bba18e172331c.png 1125w,\n/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/aa440/d32bba18e172331c.png 1500w,\n/static/b21202d494db900379ce0b616fd3fd2e/bfe1f/d32bba18e172331c.png 2177w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p class=\"para\">MDX编写的方式和普通markdown大同小异，也是非常简单。</p>\n<h2 class=\"heading subtitle heading\" id=\"结束语\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E8%AF%AD\" aria-label=\"结束语 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>结束语</h2>\n<p class=\"para\">到目前为止，Storybook编写文档的基本方式已经介绍得差不多了。接下来将从一个组件库出发，演示如何使用Storybook，从零搭建一个文档站点。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#mdx\">MDX</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#doc-blocks\">Doc Blocks</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#argstable\">ArgsTable</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#canvas\">Canvas</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#mdx%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90\">MDX的简单例子</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E7%9A%84mdx%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\">单纯的MDX文件</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E8%AF%AD\">结束语</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"MDX","depth":2,"value":"MDX"},{"id":"Doc-Blocks","depth":2,"value":"Doc Blocks"},{"id":"ArgsTable","depth":3,"value":"ArgsTable"},{"id":"Canvas","depth":3,"value":"Canvas"},{"id":"MDX的简单例子","depth":2,"value":"MDX的简单例子"},{"id":"单纯的MDX文件","depth":2,"value":"单纯的MDX文件"},{"id":"结束语","depth":2,"value":"结束语"}],"frontmatter":{"title":"Storybook 使用手册——MDX 和 Doc Blocks","date":"2022-04-24","cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512850183-6d7990f42385?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=85&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=srgb","description":null,"categories":["技术研究"],"tags":["JavaScrtipt","CSS","Storybook"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blogs/「译」衡量Web性能，多快才算快？/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"「译」衡量Web性能，多快才算快？"}},"next":{